HTVdev,provides,resources,to,develop,ideas,and,applications,within,HTC,devices,It,also,enables,connection,with,HTC,and,other,developers,The,HTC,Common,Controls,API,extends,the,existing,set,of,Android,widgets,with,a,suite,of,customized,general,purpose,controls,By,reusing,these,common,controls,application,and,widget,developers,can,create,an,HTC,look,and,feel,to,applications